      <h3 class="c-entry-box-base__headline"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.polygon.com/baldurs-gate-3-guides/23832181/he-who-was-madeline-bg3-forgive-punish-ledger-wicked">Should you side with He Who Was or Madeline in Baldur’s Gate 3</a></h3>
    

  
    
      
